DOSAGE AND DIRECTIONS FOR USE
Terra-Cortril (oxytetracycline and hydrocortisone)  Eye/Ear Suspension:
Terra-Cortril (oxytetracycline and hydrocortisone)  Eye/Ear Ointment: 
The patient should be instructed to avoid contamination of the tip of the tube when instilling the suspension or the ointment. The suspension should be shaken well before use. The dropper should be replaced in the bottle immediately after use.
